{"id": "1330941130447126558", "channel_id": "1330941130447126558", "type": 0, "author_id": "1274188474957828132", "author_name": "yingmai_", "author_bot": false, "content": "脑缸组你们周边真不考虑通贩一下吗？一张哈姆林镭射票能185不包拍出去，特h价\n炒成这样真觉得做周边没市场吗？\n现在周年礼盒也基本都是700  800拍出去，\n这个价能做几套周年礼盒？你游这么点人炒的比超级烫圈还恐怖。\n你真出了包挣的，\n你游想吃官谷的真的很多，吃谷人费劲心思吃不到谷，官方费劲心思结果钱都让黄牛挣走了，\n只有黄牛对天大笑此游能让我大赚特赚，下回还炒。\n除了黄牛都受伤的世界达成了，通贩不了也起码约束一下吧。", "timestamp": "2025-01-20T16:44:53.189000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 11}], "attachments": [{"id": "1330941130778349629", "filename": "IMG_8294.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 81972, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1330941130447126558/1330941130778349629/IMG_8294.jpg?ex=6a00b605&is=69ff6485&hm=9ade03d6a4d470609856ac2f124a874fefe7c64d99e7fec00b1dfd5323952495&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1330941130447126558", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "脑缸能不能给我们表演一下背刺黄牛", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1330758228807647253", "channel_id": "1330758228807647253", "type": 0, "author_id": "694573382380945529", "author_name": "craux.", "author_bot": false, "content": "As for the current ranking system, I feel it's a bit painful for higher ranks. because when we lose, we get deducted like -170 point, but if we win we only get +60 or even worse +20ish. It took a long time to climb just to lose once and getting alot of minus.\n\nMaybe we can have a ranking system based on stars like:\n- Bronze 3 (need 3 stars to Bronze 2)\n- Bronze 2 ...\n- Bronze 1 ...\n- Silver 3 ...\n\nThis way it doesn't hurt for higher ranks because they only get -1 star for losing a game.", "timestamp": "2025-01-20T04:38:06.040000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1330758228807647253", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "traphase ranking system rework", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
